        <p>
            AEEA`s first application now allows you to manage all your accounts from just one device! Organisation and simplicity are the key elements that define our product.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn myButton" href="https://www.ing.ro/persoane-fizice">Visit ING &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Transfer safely</h2>
        <p>Our application ensures that all your transactions are done completely safe in the shortest time possible.</p>
        <p><a class="btn myButton" href="https://www.bcr.ro/ro/persoane-fizice">Visit BCR &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Pay domestic bills</h2>
        <p>Now you can pay domestic bills with a simple online transaction!</p>
        <p><a class="btn myButton" href="https://www.brd.ro/">Visit BRD &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>